### Create new recipe
POST http://localhost:7070/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Frikadelle-opskrift",
  "instructions": "1. Hak løg. 2. Bland med kød. 3. Steg.",
  "ingredients": [
    { "name": "Hakket svinekød", "amount": "400g" },
    { "name": "Løg", "amount": "1 stk" },
    { "name": "Mel", "amount": "2 spsk" }
  ]
}

### Get recipe by ID
GET http://localhost:7070/api/recipes/1

### Update recipe title
PATCH http://localhost:7070/api/recipes/1/title
Content-Type: text/plain

Frikadelle-opskrift deluxe

### Delete recipe
DELETE http://localhost:7070/api/recipes/1
